<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Handy-Hilfe für Senioren – Persönliche Unterstützung</title>
  
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    
    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
      background: #0a0a0a;
      color: #e0e0e0;
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-size: 20px;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }
    
    .container {
      max-width: 960px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 25px;
    }
    
    header {
      background: rgba(20, 20, 20, 0.65);
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      padding: 80px 0 60px;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(20px);
      transition: opacity 1.3s ease-out, transform 1.6s ease-out;
    }
    
    header.visible {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
    
    h1 {
      font-size: 3.8rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #ffffff;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }
    
    h2 {
      font-size: 2.6rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #f0f0f0;
      margin: 80px 0 40px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .subtitle {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      color: #bbbbbb;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      font-weight: 300;
    }
    
    .cta-button {
      display: inline-block;
      background: rgba(40, 40, 40, 0.9);
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      padding: 18px 48px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
    }
    
    .cta-button:hover {
      background: rgba(60, 60, 60, 0.95);
      transform: translateY(-4px);
      border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    }
    
    .glass-card {
      background: rgba(30, 30, 30, 0.55);
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 32px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.35);
      
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(50px);
      transition: opacity 1.1s ease-out, transform 1.4s ease-out;
    }
    
    .glass-card.visible {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
    
    .services {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(340px, 1fr));
      gap: 30px;
      margin: 40px 0;
    }
    
    .service-card h3 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      color: #ffffff;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    
    .service-card p {
      color: #cccccc;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }
    
    .prices table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      margin: 40px 0;
      color: #dddddd;
    }
    
    .prices th, .prices td {
      padding: 18px 20px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      text-align: left;
    }
    
    .prices th {
      background: rgba(40,40,40,0.4);
      color: #ffffff;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    
    .about {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 60px 0;
    }
    
    .about img {
      width: 220px;
      height: 220px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      object-fit: cover;
      border: 3px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      margin-bottom: 32px;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    }
    
    .contact-form {
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      padding: 40px;
    }
    
    label {
      display: block;
      margin: 24px 0 10px;
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #eeeeee;
    }
    
    input, textarea {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 14px 18px;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      background: rgba(40,40,40,0.6);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      border-radius: 10px;
      color: white;
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    }
    
    input:focus, textarea:focus {
      outline: none;
      border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    }
    
    footer {
      background: #000000;
      color: #888888;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 60px 0 40px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    }
    
    footer a {
      color: #bbbbbb;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    
    footer a:hover {
      color: #ffffff;
    }
    
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      h1 { font-size: 2.8rem; }
      h2 { font-size: 2.2rem; }
      .cta-button { font-size: 1.3rem; padding: 16px 40px; }
      body { font-size: 18px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Handy-Hilfe für Senioren</h1>
    <div class="subtitle">Persönlich. Geduldig. Bei Ihnen zuhause.</div>
    
    <p style="font-size:1.4rem; max-width:720px; margin:0 auto 40px; color:#cccccc;">
      Individuelle Unterstützung bei Smartphone, Tablet, WhatsApp, Fotos, Internet und Sicherheit – klar, ohne Fachbegriffe.
    </p>
    
    <a href="tel:+49123456789" class="cta-button">Termin vereinbaren</a>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="container">

  <h2>Meine Leistungen</h2>
  <div class="services">
    <div class="glass-card service-card">
      <h3>Telefon & Kontakte</h3>
      <p>Nummern speichern, Anrufe tätigen, Klingeltöne einstellen, Freisprechen nutzen</p>
    </div>
    <div class="glass-card service-card">
      <h3>WhatsApp & Nachrichten</h3>
      <p>Nachrichten schreiben, Bilder & Sprachnachrichten versenden, Gruppen verstehen</p>
    </div>
    <div class="glass-card service-card">
      <h3>Fotos & Kamera</h3>
      <p>Fotos aufnehmen, betrachten, sortieren, an Familie senden</p>
    </div>
    <div class="glass-card service-card">
      <h3>Internet & Apps</h3>
      <p>Einfaches Surfen, YouTube, Wetter, Nachrichten-Apps bedienen</p>
    </div>
    <div class="glass-card service-card">
      <h3>Sicherheit & Schutz</h3>
      <p>Betrugsmaschen erkennen, Passwörter sicher nutzen, Updates verstehen</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2>Preise</h2>
  <div class="glass-card prices">
    <table>
      <tr><th>Leistung</th><th>Dauer</th><th>Preis</th></tr>
      <tr><td>Einzeltermin</td><td>ca. 60 Minuten</td><td>25 €</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Paket 3 Termine</td><td>3 × ca. 60 Min</td><td>70 €</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Sicherheits-Check (Zusatz)</td><td>ca. 30 Min</td><td>10 €</td></tr>
    </table>
  </div>
  
  <div style="text-align:center; margin:70px 0 100px;">
    <a href="tel:+49123456789" class="cta-button">Jetzt Termin vereinbaren</a>
  </div>

  <div class="about">
    <h2>Über mich</h2>
    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/220x220/222/eee?text=Ihr+Name" alt="Ihr Berater">
    
    <p style="font-size:1.4rem; max-width:720px; margin:0 auto; color:#cccccc;">
      Ich bin <strong>[Ihr Name]</strong>.<br>
      Mit viel Geduld und klarer Sprache unterstütze ich seit Jahren Senioren dabei, ihre Geräte sicher und selbstständig zu nutzen – direkt bei Ihnen zu Hause.
    </p>
  </div>

  <h2>Kontakt</h2>
  <div class="glass-card contact-form">
    <form action="mailto:deine@email.de" method="post" enctype="text/plain">
      <label for="name">Name</label>
      <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>
      
      <label for="phone">Telefon</label>
      <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" required>
      
      <label for="topic">Thema / Anliegen</label>
      <textarea id="topic" name="topic" rows="4" placeholder="z. B. WhatsApp einrichten, Fotos versenden lernen..."></textarea>
      
      <label for="time">Wann würde es passen?</label>
      <input type="text" id="time" name="time" placeholder="z. B. dienstags Vormittag">
      
      <div style="text-align:center; margin-top:50px;">
        <button type="submit" class="cta-button" style="border:none; cursor:pointer; font-size:1.4rem; padding:16px 60px;">Anfrage senden</button>
      </div>
    </form>
    
    <p style="text-align:center; margin-top:50px; font-size:1.4rem;">
      Oder direkt anrufen:<br>
      <strong style="font-size:2rem; color:#ffffff;"><a href="tel:+49123456789" style="color:inherit; text-decoration:none;">0123 456789</a></strong>
    </p>
  </div>

</div>

<footer>
  <div class="container">
    <p>Handy-Hilfe für Senioren • [Ihr Name] • © 2026</p>
    <p style="margin-top:20px;">
      <a href="#">Impressum</a>  •  <a href="#">Datenschutz</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</footer>

<script>
  const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
    entries.forEach(entry => {
      if (entry.isIntersecting) {
        entry.target.classList.add('visible');
      }
    });
  }, {
    threshold: 0.08,
    rootMargin: "0px 0px -80px 0px"
  });

  document.querySelectorAll('header, .glass-card, .service-card').forEach(el => {
    observer.observe(el);
  });
</script>

</body>
</html>